{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A peaceful morning stroll has turned into the deadliest day of your life.</strong>\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398950/extras/sba2.png?t=1734838896\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as a young woman living in a bucolic, peaceful Slavic village who is thrust into an apocalyptic scenario: a doomsday attack on her home.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398950/extras/sba4.png?t=1734838896\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Running seems to be the only survivable option.<br>The dark depths of the nearby woods hide an even darker secret.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398950/extras/sba5.png?t=1734838896\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An encounter with a mysterious beast of a man in the woods leaves you in a heart-racing predicament. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398950/extras/sba1.png?t=1734838896\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you find a way to escape him?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Or will you learn how to dig deeper, and earn the man's trust instead?\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Choose a side; Don't look back.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>This rabbit hole goes deeper than you think.</i>\u00a0</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398950/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734838896","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398950/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1734838896","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398950/e73318671fac1301